title.rendered: STEDI DEUTSCH CONNECTORS MALE & FEMALE 2 PIN DT/DT-P

content.rendered:
2 Pin Deutsch DT and DTP connectors

DETAILS

Deutsch connectors have a built a reputation as market leaders and with solid foundation. 100% environmentally sealed, and very reliable pin contacts help eliminate wiring gremlins by fortifying your harness with Deutsch. Thermal plastic connector eliminate heat at the plugs resistant point.

The connector package includes

  1. Thermal plastic connector plug
  2. Thermal plastic connector socket
  3. Socket retainer
  4. Wedge-lock
  5. 2 x Male solid strip crimp pins
  6. 2 x Female solid strip crimp pins

We have two variants to choose from.

DT Connector: The 2 Pin DT Version is the most common and is suitable for automotive wire up to 4mm. This is the type of connector we use on our lights up to and including 200w (15A)

DTP Connector: The 2 Pin DTP Version is used for our lights over 200w and can handle continuous 25A within one shell, and accepts 6mm automotive wire.

SPECIFICATIONS

-55C TO +125C OPERATING TEMPERATURE
ENVIRONMENTALLY SEALED
RUGGED THERMAL PLASTIC SHELL
INTEGRAL CONNECTOR LATCH

 

WHAT’S IN THE BOX

  • Deutsch DT or DTP connector set
